{
  "chapter": 54,
  "chapter_summary": "第七回 同是天涯沦落人\n\n本章讲述了陆小凤在幽灵山庄与花寡妇的深夜对话。花寡妇向陆小凤坦白了自己的过去，揭露了她与老刀把子的关系。随后，表哥（顾飞云）出现并试图杀害他们，但被海奇阔和管家婆阻止。表哥揭露了自己是巴山剑客的传人，受命潜入幽灵山庄调查老刀把子的身份。老刀把子最终现身，放走了陆小凤和花寡妇。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你当然也听人说过我是条母狗，会吃人的母狗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你为什么还不上来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不敢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能将淮南柳家的独门真气，和点苍秘传",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "融而为一的人并不多，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也知道我跟谢坚四个最好的朋友都上过床？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然你什么都知道了，为什么还不上来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我不高兴，也因为你管不着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来你这个人果然跟别的男人有点不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来，我请你喝酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他认为你跟这地方别的男人都上过床。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在这里一个都没有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只有一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么不问我这个人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我为什么要问？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她的笑容忽又消失：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是后来你变了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "变的不是我，是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可怕？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她的手握紧，眼中有泪珠滚下：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说的是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说的是老刀把子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老刀把子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她笑了笑，笑得很凄凉：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你献身给他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我甚至可以为他牺牲一切，就算他叫我去死，我也会去死的，可是……可是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是我并不喜欢他，我……我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若是你，我也会这么样做的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "再喝只怕就要醉了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "醉了又何妨？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "假如真的能醉，我更感激你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老实告诉你，我也早就想痛痛快快的大醉一次。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想不到？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的确想不到。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想不到的还有很多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是现在我总算已都想通了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我才知道是你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜谁也想不到竟然是我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他有把握：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实我也知道你恨我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你喜欢男人，男人喜欢的却是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许我还有别的理由。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么理由？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许我是为了要替老钩子出气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你刚才是不是说要把这笔账推到我头上来？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_qi_kuo",
      "speaker_name": "海奇阔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你想杀他们，又怕老刀把子不答应。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_qi_kuo",
      "speaker_name": "海奇阔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实我也一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_qi_kuo",
      "speaker_name": "海奇阔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也一样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_qi_kuo",
      "speaker_name": "海奇阔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我比你运气好，我找到了一个替我背黑锅的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_qi_kuo",
      "speaker_name": "海奇阔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_qi_kuo",
      "speaker_name": "海奇阔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要我替你去杀了陆小凤？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_qi_kuo",
      "speaker_name": "海奇阔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不肯？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_qi_kuo",
      "speaker_name": "海奇阔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时你杀了他，可以要我替你背黑锅，现在呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_qi_kuo",
      "speaker_name": "海奇阔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我若不肯去杀他，你就会杀了我。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你果然是个明白人，所以我一直都很喜欢你。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若去杀了他，你就肯放了我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_qi_kuo",
      "speaker_name": "海奇阔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不像。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知不知道花寡妇是个很厉害、很不好惹的女人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_qi_kuo",
      "speaker_name": "海奇阔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么我刚才为什么要对她出手？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_qi_kuo",
      "speaker_name": "海奇阔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_qi_kuo",
      "speaker_name": "海奇阔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我要你们认为我的武功很差劲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_qi_kuo",
      "speaker_name": "海奇阔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实我一招就可以杀了你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不会杀人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你就不如赶快让我杀了你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你就是巴山剑客惟一的衣钵传人顾飞云？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "巴山神剑，果然是好剑法。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本来就是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你当然也想不通，我为什么要杀了他们，却不杀你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_dao_ba_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老刀把子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以他们故意要你被西门吹雪逼得无路可走？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里的合约金要十万两？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为了买回自己的一条命，十万两并不算多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "的确不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "连他们都不知道老刀把子的来历和底细？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有人知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个人是什么人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来接应我的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你等得着急，就只好先去找他们？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已找过十二个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你全都找错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我只好杀了他们灭口。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一次你认为我就是来接应你的人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只希望这一次没有错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也希望你这一次没有错。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不能说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你根本就不知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们看起来都不怕死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然已非死不可，害怕又有什么用？只不过……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只不过你不想死得太糊涂而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然我们已非死不可，你说出来又有何妨？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你笑什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我在笑你，你明明知道的，又何必来问我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想拖我下水？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我为什么要找替死鬼？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这的确是个圈套，被套进去的人却不是我，是你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_biao_ge",
      "speaker_name": "表哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们都是人才，我佩服你们。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到他真的一点也不怕死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有种人更不能做！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_dao_ba_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老刀把子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_dao_ba_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老刀把子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你就是这种人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_dao_ba_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老刀把子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我一向很有自知之明。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_dao_ba_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老刀把子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你替我惹的麻烦的确不少……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_dao_ba_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老刀把子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但是你绝不能杀我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_dao_ba_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老刀把子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_dao_ba_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老刀把子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "守口如瓶，永不泄漏这里的秘密。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_dao_ba_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老刀把子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我答应。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_dao_ba_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老刀把子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我信任你，你走吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_dao_ba_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老刀把子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要我走？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_dao_ba_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老刀把子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算主人不能杀客人，至少总能请客人走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是外面……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论我要什么都行？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_dao_ba_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老刀把子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要你能带走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要带她走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不怕？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怕什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gua_fu",
      "speaker_name": "花寡妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我反正已死过一次，再死一次又何妨？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    }
